original_query: SELECT mi.movie_id, mk.movie_id FROM keyword AS k, movie_info AS mi, movie_keyword AS mk, title AS t WHERE k.keyword LIKE '%sequel%' AND mi.info IN ('Sweden', 'Norway', 'Germany', 'Denmark', 'Swedish', 'Denish', 'Norwegian', 'German', 'USA', 'American') AND t.production_year > 1990 AND t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
rewritten_query: CREATE VIEW E3 AS SELECT movie_keyword.movie_id AS E3_movie_id,movie_keyword.keyword_id AS E3_keyword_id FROM movie_keyword AS movie_keyword

CREATE VIEW E2 AS SELECT movie_info.movie_id AS E2_movie_id FROM movie_info AS movie_info WHERE movie_info.info IN ('American', 'Denish', 'Denmark', 'German', 'Germany', 'Norway', 'Norwegian', 'Sweden', 'Swedish', 'USA')
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E3_stage1_0 AS SELECT * FROM E3 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E2 WHERE E3.E3_movie_id=E2.E2_movie_id)
CREATE VIEW E1 AS SELECT keyword.id AS E1_id FROM keyword AS keyword WHERE keyword.keyword LIKE '%sequel%'
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E3_stage1_1 AS SELECT * FROM E3_stage1_0 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E1 WHERE E3_stage1_0.E3_keyword_id=E1.E1_id)
CREATE VIEW E4 AS SELECT title.id AS E4_id FROM title AS title WHERE title.production_year > 1990
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E3_stage1_2 AS SELECT * FROM E3_stage1_1 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E4 WHERE E3_stage1_1.E3_movie_id=E4.E4_id)
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E2_stage2_0 AS SELECT * FROM E2 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E3_stage1_2 WHERE E3_stage1_2.E3_movie_id=E2.E2_movie_id)
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E1_stage2_0 AS SELECT * FROM E1 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E3_stage1_2 WHERE E3_stage1_2.E3_keyword_id=E1.E1_id)
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E4_stage2_0 AS SELECT * FROM E4 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E3_stage1_2 WHERE E3_stage1_2.E3_movie_id=E4.E4_id)

CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E_stage3 AS SELECT E3_stage1_2.E3_movie_id AS E3_movie_id, E2_stage2_0.E2_movie_id AS E2_movie_id FROM E3_stage1_2, E2_stage2_0, E1_stage2_0, E4_stage2_0 WHERE E3_stage1_2.E3_movie_id=E2_stage2_0.E2_movie_id AND E3_stage1_2.E3_keyword_id=E1_stage2_0.E1_id AND E3_stage1_2.E3_movie_id=E4_stage2_0.E4_id
